  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO AMEND SECTION 47-7-37, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, TO AUTHORIZE AN INTERVENTION COURT TO IMPOSE UP TO THE REMAINDER OF THE SUSPENDED PORTION OF A PROBATIONER'S SENTENCE WITHOUT THE PROBATIONER HAVING A HEARING UNDER THIS SECTION UPON THE JUDGE'S WRITTEN FINDING OF A CERTAIN NUMBER OF VIOLATIONS OF THE PROCEDURES AND REQUIREMENTS OF THE INTERVENTION COURT; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
